{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a criminal offence to drive a private vehicle belching out black smoke.",
        "additional_details": "I have frequently had to get well away from the road as a vehicle pouring out black smoke from its exhaust has passed. I have seen pedestrians at our village pedestrian crossing engulfed in black smoke as it passed.There is a regular occurrence of these vehicles in  our area and undoubtedly it is a national problem. I have tried reporting these to the police,DVLA and DVSA but apparently they are only interested in commercial vehicles being reported.",
        "background": "There are numerous occasions on which I have seen private vehicles driving around with black smoke pouring out from the exhaust.  These vehicles need taking off the road and fixed before their MOT is due.",
